snippet.title: Pokémon PD (SNES bootleg)
snippet.description:
I managed to play this by using a patch by d4s that cracks the copy protection. (Yes, it has copy protection.)
The patch is at http://www.dforce3000.de/snes.html (No longer available. But this isn't a very good game anyway.)
Actually, in the forum post where I learned about it, he said his patch is several years old!

Comments are disabled because I mostly don't care for hearing how crappy or lame a game this is.
